name: Karakuri Daigongen mdl 00X "Bureibu"
desc:
1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner Machine monsters
If this card is Synchro Summoned: You can Special Summon 1 "Karakuri" monster from your Deck. Your Defense Position monsters cannot be destroyed by battle. Once per turn, if the battle position of a face-up "Karakuri" monster you control is changed (except during the Damage Step): You can target 1 card your opponent controls; banish it.
